Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.96,0:00:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Black Organization member who infiltrated the hospital where Mizunashi Rena is being hospitalized...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusada Rikumichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.30,0:00:11.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Killed himself after the FBI agent Akai and I cornered him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.01,0:00:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agent Akai claimed that if Kusada was able to make contact, the Organization would single out this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:23.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The FBI needed to perfect their plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.44,0:00:27.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of patients that can't be moved from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can we just wait here, knowing the Organization is coming, without alerting them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We won't just "wait."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:37.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll draw back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:38.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Draw back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:41.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean leave her here and run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.16,0:00:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll draw back our bows and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.08,0:00:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not ambush them?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.96,0:00:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The black wolves who've come to retrieve their straying colleague?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:01:02.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We discovered that Agent Akai snuck into the Black Organization in the past, and became the boyfriend of Haibara's older sister, Miyano Akemi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:09.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I'm able to escape from the Organization like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.11,0:01:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you go out with me as my real boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.91,0:01:22.41,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Dai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...\N\NIf I'm able to escape from\Nthe Organization like this,\Nas my real boyfriend?\N\NAkemi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.96,0:01:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's about how we plan to attack them, I'm still thinking it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:35.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.34,0:01:37.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I saw you, I was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.14,0:01:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just maybe you were thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:42.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:52.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, the one searching for his older sister, Hondou Eisuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.98,0:01:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Located Mizunashi Rena's hospital room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:01:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.49,0:02:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizunashi Rena.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't wake up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.12,0:02:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't ask you where my sister Hidemi is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.25,0:02:10.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:13.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're going take you somewhere again, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.92,0:02:16.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before that happens, open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.51,0:02:17.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:21.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.97,0:02:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.93,0:02:28.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.02,0:02:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:34.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you one of the new agents?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Andre Camel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.66,0:02:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I have a call from my wife right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.03,0:02:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a strategy session.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:54.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.94,0:03:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You never fail to amaze, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:16.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad you're an ally, Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.12,0:03:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now, Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In this match...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's live-or-die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.64,0:03:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.79,0:04:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tingling suspense is building.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:13.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Running in the darkness —\ha red scream and a black shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victory hinges on some strange incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Each of them are related to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:44.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan is brought to you by these sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.18,0:05:56.81,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,CLASH OF RED AND BLACK\NDISTURBANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.98,0:05:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've prepared stretchers for the patients...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.81,0:06:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And three vans to transport them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the worst arises, we'll confuse them and flee with Mizunashi Rena in tow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I do hope we don't have to resort to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are there any questions?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:18.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.29,0:06:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About communicating...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.96,0:06:23.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No cell phones or wireless devices, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, with this being a hospital, they can affect the medical equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.55,0:06:31.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, cell phone calls are easy to tap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.97,0:06:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should anything happen, report it to your block leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your leader will then go outside and contact James via radio, who will be waiting in the parking lot to give instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't this too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.28,0:06:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we play the phone game with them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They could end up taking vital tofu from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.41,0:06:57.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we are already prepared for an escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps it's best we go for it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is our absolute last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.92,0:07:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since they still don't know which room is Mizunashi Rena's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moving her now is too risky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.01,0:07:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They definitely have their eyes on every car that comes and goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:22.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that we know their member Kusada was hiding an infrared thermographic device that detects heat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's likely that they'll discover which is our car from the number of people inside, thus making the FBI targets for their snipers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should that happen, we'll be escaping from bullets as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what if we need to contact you in an emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:44.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, contact me on my wireless if needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave that call to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:53.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, they likely won't come here wielding machine guns and handguns openly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They don't want the world to know of their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:04.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Creeping as if a shadow, vanishing like the fog...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's their trademark tactic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The strategy session is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.99,0:08:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:22.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already know the plan from seeing the three stretchers here and the vans in the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't say it's a "good" plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.75,0:08:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was expected, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:35.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,J-Just what is with you two!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.26,0:08:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:41.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it time for you to go home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:45.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told them I'd be staying at the Professor's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already took a quick nap, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:49.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:59.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us know when you decide to flee, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.50,0:09:03.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm confident in my driving technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.29,0:09:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.71,0:09:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you seen that man before?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:13.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He only joined us recently, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:17.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, but I don't recognize his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:23.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would never forget an enemy face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.43,0:09:26.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's natural for him to appear recognizable.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:29.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is a fellow FBI agent, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I still have a bad feeling about him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.58,0:09:47.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't getting much sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:51.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are bags under your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I'll go out for some fresh air while you patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.30,0:10:02.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought, Shuu...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.56,0:10:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's thinking too much about his murdered girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.85,0:10:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, with him, all we need is him thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.94,0:10:15.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since he has been with them and understands their mindset...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's an opponent whose life they've already made multiple attempts on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.45,0:10:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the FBI's definitive trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.72,0:10:44.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My stomach...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.14,0:10:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.10,0:10:48.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.40,0:10:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Toto line train is now arriving at Platform No. 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait behind the white line patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.74,0:11:00.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-My throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.86,0:11:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That strange smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:05.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Station attendant, please call for an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:11.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I can't get that notebook back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.71,0:11:13.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone's hearts will break!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:16.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fire has broken out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.09,0:11:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please follow the instructions of the nearby attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:29.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,James Black{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we don't have a patient by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.40,0:11:39.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not for a patient —\hit's for an attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:42.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is a friend of mine, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.16,0:11:43.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.95,0:11:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm here to deliver it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.78,0:11:47.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who sent you and what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.91,0:11:50.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sender was...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One Kusada Rikumichi it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kusada Rikumichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.97,0:12:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep, you can guess what Kusada{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} sent just from the outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.72,0:12:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Columbine...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:13.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's known as "Odamaki" in Japan, I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.77,0:12:15.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sent this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since they used the name of their member who killed himself last night, there's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.49,0:12:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a precaution, we acted as security guards and checked all luggage of those entering the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We even checked delivery packages.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.91,0:12:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would they send this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.75,0:12:36.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Columbine is a flower that grows in Colorado...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.46,0:12:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Obtain without failure."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.71,0:12:40.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the language of that flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:44.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it also means "clear victory."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a declaration of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.76,0:12:50.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.48,0:12:53.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:54.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're at the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.81,0:13:00.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are they fire victims from earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Meier at the entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:06.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.87,0:13:07.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.08,0:13:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So many ill patients and others are flooding the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.41,0:13:13.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't check them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:16.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:35.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those coming in are claiming there were three accidents that occurred simultaneously in the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three accidents at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.27,0:13:39.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Food poisoning, a disturbing odor, and a fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.03,0:13:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it their doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:48.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But while it's easy to control the timing of a disturbing odor and a fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Food poisoning symptoms show up at varying times from person to person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:55.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps they used a drug that emulates the appearance of food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:14:04.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just the same, the other two accidents were set up in order to avoid killing anyone but also ensure they came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, after excluding those with surface injuries such as burns or cuts...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's still difficult to determine who is faking pain in their stomach, throat, and eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.10,0:14:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They can pretend to be victims of the accidents so as to get a large number of members into the hospital and quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their goal is, indeed, to locate the room where Mizunashi Rena is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they search in waves, they could find her very quickly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:37.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.12,0:14:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they're sending members in large numbers like that and having them act so suspiciously...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.30,0:14:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then they are giving us FBI agents a chance to apprehend some of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are not the types to take such risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.60,0:14:54.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, this uproar...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their target may be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.10,0:14:58.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear something just then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.83,0:15:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the flower pot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And even worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.25,0:15:19.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's getting louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, there is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.29,0:15:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Put it on the ground and step away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You didn't even check the inside of the pot?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.21,0:16:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We thought they were only flowers, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:17.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Planting a bomb in a flower pot like this could only take out a few agents.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the explosion drew the Japanese police, searching for Mizunashi Rena would be difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They could gain nothing from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what you thought, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we have to get rid of the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.41,0:16:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's rigged with numerous traps, so defusing it will take too long.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:41.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The best and safest option is to take it to an unoccupied area and let it explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the timer is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have 31 minutes and 14 seconds before it goes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.25,0:16:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, forgive me, but it's up to you, Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.59,0:16:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, Shuu, you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.97,0:16:55.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:59.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a garbage dump seven kilos from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go by car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:02.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then take my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:07.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you really have the time to make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.90,0:17:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The main roads are backed up due to the traffic caused by the three incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Making it in thirty minutes is questionable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.28,0:17:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that is, unless you had a navigator like me with knowledge of the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.58,0:17:22.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:23.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing away from your post?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.04,0:17:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard of the traffic problem with so many flooding the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:34.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to report, since my post is nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I figured it was easier to approach you all directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.64,0:17:39.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no time to argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two get that bomb out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.64,0:17:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Camel{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:50.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, he doesn't have the friendliest face, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.90,0:17:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were gracious enough to include a visible timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:18:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, it was made to get louder so we would notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, isn't it strange that they gave us more than thirty minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.96,0:18:13.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's as if they gave the FBI enough time to take the bomb elsewhere to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.63,0:18:16.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, what was the bomb meant for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what are they trying to do here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:32.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does this really lead to a shortcut to the dump?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.78,0:18:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was completely empty two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.78,0:18:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.03,0:18:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, did you put a clock in the trunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been hearing this ticking sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.96,0:18:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should have mentioned that earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.96,0:18:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.09,0:18:57.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There isn't a clock back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.55,0:19:01.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you really hear that back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and get in before I leave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:11.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you in the driver's seat now!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.73,0:19:16.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be too tiring to direct you to the secret path aloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:17.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm better than you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.78,0:19:22.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, there isn't a lot of time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.78,0:19:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you lie about the clock sound in the trunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.33,0:19:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, sometimes lying is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:34.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on to it tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.89,0:19:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, the dump is the other way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I gave up on that idea due to time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All we need is an unoccupied place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and look at my kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot, I was here first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, those delivery men...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:14.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there are a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.50,0:20:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.63,0:20:19.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.30,0:20:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.51,0:20:25.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusada Rikumichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:33.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everything going well on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bomb should be going off soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.69,0:20:36.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Agent Camel took the wheel...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why open the roof?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:48.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:50.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please take the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:09.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that noise!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.47,0:21:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:13.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, we've disposed of the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Great job, Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:17.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:22.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anything deserves praise, it's Agent Camel's driving technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.20,0:21:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how are things on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:33.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} seem to have found a clue as to what they're after.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm from security.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A nurse just brought you a package, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.38,0:21:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.47,0:21:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it from someone named Kusada?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I don't know anyone by that name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, allow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I thought: another bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.61,0:22:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a listening device.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.24,0:22:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They use it for a rising remittance fraud method.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.12,0:22:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-Bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.00,0:22:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there really are bombs in those gifts?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.33,0:22:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of these plastic explosives will only blow one room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.67,0:22:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if all of them go off at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.88,0:22:29.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The entire hospital will come down without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four hours remain until the bombs delivered to the hospital go off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.81,0:24:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We, after becoming aware of their aim, have come up with a risky plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.99,0:24:14.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,CLASH OF RED AND BLACK\NDISGUISE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.99,0:24:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time, on Detective Conan...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.74,0:24:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan was brought to you by these sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.51,0:24:34.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Driving Technique
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.51,0:24:31.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.59,0:24:34.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Driving Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.89,0:24:36.43,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,March 3rd is "mimi no hi."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.41,0:24:37.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's also called Hinamatsuri, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.16,0:24:38.27,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Because it's a day for chicks.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.24,0:24:39.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
